<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.2">
<l>kārum vārpaṉik kaṭalu maṉṉavaṉ</l>
<l>tāru mārvamuṅ kaṇṭa taṇṭamō</l>
<l>cōru māmukil tuḷiyi ṉūṭuvan</l>
<l>tīra vāṭaitā ṉīru meṉṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is [my] punishment [now that I] saw the garland and the chest</l>
<l>Of him like a dark cloud and the vast, cold sea,</l>
<l>That the sharp north wind, driving between the drops of rain</l>
<l>From the teeming dark clouds, pierces me?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
